# 🧾 Mandera Soft POS (Desktop App)

A fast, reliable, and easy-to-use Point of Sale (POS) system built for modern businesses.
Designed for performance, simplicity, and real-world retail environments.

---

##  Download

 **Download the latest version here:**
[Download Mandera Soft POS](#)

> Replace `#` with your GitHub release link

---

##  Features

*  Sales & checkout management
*  Inventory tracking
*  Customer management
*  Reports & analytics
*  Works with hosted backend (cloud-powered)
*  Fast desktop performance (Electron-based)

---

## 🖥 System Requirements

* Windows 10 / Windows 11
* Minimum 4GB RAM
* Internet connection required (for backend sync)

---

##  Installation

1. Download the `.exe` installer
2. Double-click to install
3. Launch the app from Start Menu
4. Login with your account

---

##  Security

* Secure authentication
* Data handled through protected backend APIs
* No sensitive data stored locally without authorization

---

##  Updates

New versions will be released regularly with improvements and new features.
Make sure to download the latest version from this page.

